{"tid":1816540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀不滿政府未能解釋《香港人權與民主法案》對港影響","createTime":"2020-01-08T10:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T08:30:07.000Z","uid":212626,"like":183,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff037067223b85dee57e04aab1c157480abcd5d","tid":1816540,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:02:45.000Z","msg":"美國通過《香港人權與民主法案》，署理商務及經濟發展局局長陳百里重申並無必要。本港駐美國的多個經貿辦過去曾與約240名美國官員、國會議員及幕僚，解說香港奉行自由經濟及本況實際情況，澄清誤解，強調雙方關係互惠互利。<br />\n<br />\n新民黨葉劉淑儀於立法會會議，要求陳百里解釋法案第5條對本港的影響，陳百里表示手上沒有有關條文，葉劉淑儀感到失望，她不滿到立法會回應質詢的官員，未曾參閱法案內容。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨議員郭榮鏗批評，行政長官林鄭月娥曾經取消與推動法案的參議員會面，放棄解說機會。陳百里表示，政府一直嘗試游說，但面對複雜國際經貿環境，有外國議員因為選舉導向或政治取態，只願聽取意念相近的意見，重申即使香港面對社會挑戰，法治、言論自由、資金流通自由都沒有受損。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501676-20200108.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501676-20200108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=f0a0f124\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501676-20200108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c4de082b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501676-20200108.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ad7d4cd37da5c141c2751a1f5d85e7c37c9ae96c","tid":1816540,"uid":117276,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae75d0c728e6056c008a7368d6092ba98288642d","tid":1816540,"uid":50801,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:06:53.000Z","msg":"葉劉就快瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77454e65b5098dad8313877b8c44cf5d0cff