><br />\n自衞隊身體質素＆勇氣全世界都大有必要<br />\n香港人 only you can change yourself<br />\n未來嘅希望由我地做起<br />\n<br />\nStep 9.建立自信 增肌增體能<br />\n同敵人對抗 除左夠體能<br />\n最緊要隨時作戰救人心態<br />\n並不容許你食花生<br />\n⚡️減少重複接觸影響自己的負面人事<br />\n🍎做應該做嘅事<br />\n🔥要增肌/提神/搵工/調理身體自己埋位學<br />\n🍳訂好目標 全力以赴<br />\n<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\n啱嘅就聽下 唔啱聽我都唔會覆你 <br />\n重點係大家Build up自信＋能耐大返對家 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民認真</span></span> <br />\n依家風頭火勢 好多五毛<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 團結 正能量<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n我地要內在夠強 大返佢地<br />\n<br />\n永續健康身心 長期抗爭致勝<br />\n營養/心態歡迎搵我幫手<br />\n教完大家要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有需TG 唔問名 <br />\n幫你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動打仗飲食法<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n支持升級黃圈 培訓人才人人出資資助小朋友就業<br />\n免費同收費我都做 支持黃圈返正價出錢幫人<br />\n得閒係屋企/搵我做下運動放鬆<br />\nBuild up 自己自信 無狗敢搞你<br />\n如果你期望唔出付就會有結果<br />\n請你離開<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=a3fe8d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FtreehoHealthAdvice&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=754bff99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice</a><br />\n討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/THHATalk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTHHATalk&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=62c956e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/THHATalk</a><br />\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif